query:
INSERT INTO contents (item_id, raw_html, raw_text, lang, extracted_at, checksum)
                    VALUES ($1, $2, NULL, NULL, NOW(), $3)
                    ON CONFLICT (item_id) 
                    DO UPDATE SET 
                        raw_html = EXCLUDED.raw_html,
                        extracted_at = EXCLUDED.extracted_at,
                        checksum = EXCLUDED.checksum
